---
---
<div class="video-grid">
  <div class="video-text">
    <div class="section-meta">
      <span class="section-number">05</span>
      <span class="section-label">Nos événements en vidéo</span>
    </div>
    <h2>Revivez l'ambiance de nos événements</h2>
    <p>
      Hackathon, job dating, ateliers de code — retrouvez les temps forts de Code4Sud sur notre chaîne YouTube. Témoignages d'étudiants, recruteurs et partenaires.
    </p>
    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@code4sud" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="video-cta">
      Voir la chaîne YouTube →
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="video-placeholder">
    <iframe
      width="100%"
      height="100%"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hLxFv7mttvU"
      title="Code4Sud — Nos événements en vidéo"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen
      class="video-iframe"
    ></iframe>
    <div class="video-fallback" id="video-fallback">
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@code4sud" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="play-btn" aria-label="Voir sur YouTube">
        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <p class="fallback-label">Voir sur YouTube →</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.video-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 3rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.video-text h2 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--b900);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.video-text p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--gray-secondary);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.video-cta {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--b600);
  font-weight: 400;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.12s;
}

.video-cta:hover {
  color: var(--b800);
}

.video-placeholder {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 16/9;
  background: var(--b50);
  border: 1px solid var(--b100);
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.video-iframe {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.video-fallback {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}

.play-btn {
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--b800);
  color: #fff;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.12s;
  padding-left: 3px;
}

.play-btn:hover {
  background: var(--b900);
}

.fallback-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--b600);
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .video-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
}
</style>
